            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# CodexMate 0.0.15

- Treat interrupted Desktop turns as completed activity, preventing stopped sessions from remaining stuck in the running state.
- Keep sub-agent threads grouped under their parent thread's project instead of briefly surfacing scratch workspaces as separate menu projects.
- Added regression coverage for interrupted turns and sub-agent project grouping.
]]></description>
